---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import HeroSection from "../components/Sections/HeroSection.astro";
import EventList from "../components/Sections/EventList.astro";
import SermonList from "../components/Sections/SermonList.astro";
import Button from "../components/UI/Button.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <HeroSection 
  title="Coaching & Counselling"
  subtitle="For Students, Professionals, and Organizations"
  backgroundImage="/uploads/home-header.png"
/>


<section id="intro-message" class="py-8 bg-white">
  <div class="w-full">
    <div class="px-6 md:px-16">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <h4 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">
          You know what to do — but you just can’t get yourself to do it.
        </h4>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p>
          I help you build a way of working that actually fits your brain, so you can follow through without constant stress, guilt, or last-minute panic.
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="underline hover:text-[#30B28E] transition-colors duration-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >Book</a>
          a free intro call.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- General -->
<section id="faq" class="py-8 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="w-full">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="px-6 md:px-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl prose prose-lg">
          <p>
            Does this sound familiar?
          </p>

          <ul class="green-bullets space-y-1 [&>li]:my-0">
            <li>You keep putting things off, even when they matter to you</li>
            <li>You start things last minute and end up stressed — again</li>
            <li>You make plans, but somehow don’t follow through</li>
            <li>You feel overwhelmed and don’t know where to start</li>
            <li>You’ve tried to “just be more disciplined”, but it doesn’t stick</li>
          </ul>

          <p>
            And underneath it all, there’s this thought: “I know what to do… so why can’t I just do it?”<br />
            It can feel like you’re wasting your potential and creating unnecessary stress for yourself.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center p-6">
        <img
          src="/uploads/home-image.jpg"
          alt="Coaching illustration"
          class="w-full h-auto object-contain"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<section id="faq" class="py-8 bg-white">
  <div class="w-full">
      <div class="px-6 md:px-16">
        <div class="max-w-none prose prose-lg">
          <p>
            <b>It does not have to stay that way.</b></br>
            Most advice assumes that the same methods work for everyone. But they don’t.</br>
            Instead, we figure out what works for <i>you</i>. So you can: <span class="greenDarkFont">start tasks more easily</span>, <span class="greenDarkFont">follow through more consistently</span>, <span class="greenDarkFont">build routines that actually stick</span>, <span class="greenDarkFont">work <i>with</i> your brain instead of against it</span>, and <span class="greenDarkFont">feel less overwhelmed and more in control again.</span></br>
          </p>
          <p class="mb-3">
            Through coaching and counselling, we:
          </p>

          <ul class="green-bullets my-3 space-y-1 [&>li]:my-0">
            <li>explore what is getting in your way (including resistance)</li>
            <li>test small, realistic changes </li>
            <li>adjust based on what works and what doesn’t </li>
            <li>build a system that fits your brain, your life, and your goals</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="mt-3">
            Not trying harder, but experimenting and learning what works for you.
            We will work with a mix of practical tools (habits, structure) and deeper work (patterns, beliefs, values) for <span class="greenDarkFont font-semibold">sustainable change</span>.
          </p>
          <p>
            If you recognize yourself in this, we can explore it together. 
            <a
            href="/contact"
            class="underline hover:text-[#30B28E] transition-colors duration-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >Book</a>
          a free intro call to see if we're a good fit.

          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- Individual Coaching -->
<section id="faq" class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">Coaching for Individuals</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <p>
      I offer online and in-person coaching for personal and professional questions. Sessions are practical, structured, and tailored to your needs — whether you want short-term clarity, long-term change, or a deep dive into a specific topic.
    </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a 
            href="/coaching" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-[#193472] rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-[#142a5e] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Workshops -->
<section id="faq" class="py-12 bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">Workshops for Universities & Organisations</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <p>
      I also design and deliver tailored workshops for teams, departments, and student groups on a variety of topics. Formats range from short introductions to in-depth interactive sessions.
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a 
            href="/workshops" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-[#193472] rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-[#142a5e] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
      </div>
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Why Me -->
<section id="faq" class="py-12 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-8">
      <h3 class="blueFont font-[Cambria]">Why work with me?</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">
    <p>
      My style is <b>calm, direct, practical, and empathetic.</b><br>
      I combine an analytical, scientific background with creative thinking and deep interest in how people function. 
      I don’t apply one system to everyone, but help you find what actually works for <i>you</i>.
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a 
            href="/about" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white bg-[#193472] rounded-md shadow-sm hover:bg-[#142a5e] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:ring-offset-2"
          >
            Learn More
          </a>
      </div>
    </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


